Products

Voice and Video

Mavenir offers a complete portfolio of innovative virtualized network video and voice solutions for IP based communication services.

VOICE AND VIDEO


Evolved Packet Core

Mavenir's Virtualized Evolved Packet Core (EPC) is a software-based, carrier grade solution that can be deployed on cloud-based infrastructures using Network Functions Virtualization (NFV) to rapidly scale capacity and adapt to new deployment models.

EVOLVED PACKET CORE


Mobile Messaging

Mavenir's converged messaging solutions for Rich Communication Services (RCS, RCSe), Converged IP Messaging (CPM), Short Message Service/Multimedia Messaging Service (SMS/MMS).

MOBILE MESSAGING


Mobile Client

Mavenir's Mobile Voice and Messaging Client for all devices allows Communication Service Providers to differentiate their Messaging Services

MOBILE CLIENT


RAN Virtualization

Mavenir's future-proof SmartC-RAN Solution delivers flexible cloud technologies for Radio Access Networks

RAN VIRTUALIZATION


Data Management

Mavenir is a leading provider of a data management product suite that can be deployed on carrier-grade Advanced Telecom Computing Architecture (ATCA) and commercial off-the-shelf server (COTS) hardware, or as virtualized software or cloud-based platforms.

DATA MANAGEMENT


IMS Core

IP Multimedia Subsystem (IMS) is the open standards based foundational technology for all IP communication services. With the desire to shift towards convergence and all IP networks, the adoption of IMS core technology is increasing rapidly.

IMS CORE


Diameter Signaling

Mavenir’s innovative end-to-end virtualized portfolio also includes an innovative Diameter Signaling Controller with Diameter Routing Agent (DRA) and Diameter Edge Agent (DEA) solution for LTE roaming.

DIAMETER SIGNALING


Session Border Control & Border Gateways

The Mavenir Border Gateways are carrier-grade products that can be deployed on cloud-based infrastructures using Network Functions Virtualization (NFV) to rapidly scale capacity and adapt to new deployment models. Our Border Gateways provides optimal security, flexibility, and centralization of data and voice services for operators transforming their networks to 4G LTE.

SESSION BORDER CONTROL & BORDER GATEWAYS



