Multi ID

Multi-ID, a Cloud Communications Platform for innovation in Voice, Video and Messaging

MULTI ID


Voice Over Long-Term Evolution (VOLTE)

Voice over LTE (VoLTE) empowers 4G LTE operators to offer rich voice, video and messaging services as a core offering.

VOICE OVER LONG-TERM EVOLUTION (VOLTE)


RCS Cloud Services

What’s unique about Mavenir’s RCS Cloud Services

RCS CLOUD SERVICES


Voice Over Wi-Fi (VOWIFI)

Mavenir's core network infrastructure used to deliver WiFi Calling and Messaging is the same as used to deliver VoLTE and advanced messaging.

VOICE OVER WI-FI (VOWIFI)


Voice and Video Solutions

Mavenir offers a complete portfolio of innovative virtualized network video and voice solutions for IP based communication services.

VOICE AND VIDEO SOLUTIONS


Converged IP Messaging

Mavenir offers a complete portfolio of innovative virtualized network video and voice solutions for IP based communication services.

CONVERGED IP MESSAGING


Rich Communication Services

For mobile operators launching Rich Communications Services (RCS), Mavenir's RCS solution is fully standards compliant and supports the latest GSMA RCS 5.1 specifications.

RICH COMMUNICATIONS SERVICES


Advanced Communications

Mavenir delivers critical core and access network elements required to allow service providers to continually innovate with new revenue generating services by leveraging their network as platform for development.

ADVANCED COMMUNICATIONS


Network Security

Mavenir’s security solutions are built to protect CSPs’ networks from sophisticated security threats. Mavenir’s solution, provides 360-degree security and privacy protection, addressing many types of signaling network attacks, as well as spam and fraud exploits across the network.

NETWORK SECURITY


Monetization Services

Mavenir’s portfolio of Monetization products is focused on enabling mobile operators to generate additional revenue and ARPU from their prepaid subscribers, drive subscriber engagement and improve loyalty.

MONETIZATION SERVICES


